Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tremors in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're near the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of splashing water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do. We have to turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the only path?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't any forks in the direction we were going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I lack the confidence to find my way around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll catch us even if we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They've set dogs after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So foolish-sounding, that baying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should cover your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you as many as you'd like later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:14.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fscx105\fs90\fnMailart Rubberstamp\c&H7A8995&\pos(640,456.667)}Wolf and a Silent Farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How on earth did they find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably ran into us by chance while they were looking underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they knew exactly where we were, they would have cornered us by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Milone Trading has betrayed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in running!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like we've been sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have come at a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, they can run Milone's branch office into the ground if they have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That would call for a high price indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a garden variety bluff to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we turn this corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know which—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way. We're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn left here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Almighty, please forgive my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if God forgives you, it seems that you angered Lady Luck somewhere along the way.{lit. Regret how you live you life(because it got you bad karma/luck (that caused you to miss my vitals)) before you start regretting your sins.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't moving when I called to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can smell the warmth of the sun ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you there's a way to the surface nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even notice {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course I noticed. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be at the exit once we turn right at the end of the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,An abandoned well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't think it'd end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't—you're barely standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie! I don't need my ears to know that's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered, given the description we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,, But who would have thought it'd really be you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The man behind Medio Trading is Count Ehrendott.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:17.79,Default,,1,1,0,,A large wheat-producing land is capable of designating a silver currency of their choice for all their transactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The elimination of wheat tariffs would be a blessing not only for Medio Trading and the Count,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but for those in the village as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You personally know the merchants who buy wheat from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.84,Default,TLC,0,0,0,,The village chief has entrusted everything to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheat sales reach their peak right after the harvest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We hardly got to see each other when I last visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but you met someone else, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand her over to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll present her to the Church and put the old ways to rest forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, we'll be able to destroy Milone Trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When the tariffs are lifted, the profit from our wheat will skyrocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and those we sell it to will be rich indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:25.43,Default,,1,1,0,,Lawrence, our village still remembers that you bought\Nwheat from us when we were suffering from heavy taxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be no trouble to give you purchasing priority now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawrence...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finalize this deal and open a store in this town together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As a merchant, surely you can figure gain and loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to realize that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, an honest merchant abides by his contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fate works in strange ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A peculiar wolf I've picked up wants to return to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a contract to accompany her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes against my principles to willingly breach a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry our friendship was a short one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A merchant is always saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can kill the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring {\i1}her{\i0} in alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My dagger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This might hurt a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sucking his blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid! She's only a possessed girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You gods are always like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Always making life unfair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,H...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you think those clothes you ruined cost me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're a god or not! You're going to pay for it in full!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The fifty coins left over from what you earned aren't even a fraction of what you owe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years do you think it took me to save that kind of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow you to the northlands if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your wound doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels better, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I must apologize for putting you through such danger through our ineptitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't. My companion was the cause of this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fortunate that the melee happened underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:28.02,Default,,1,1,0,,If someone else saw her in that form, our headquarters and branch stores would be ablaze by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw her true form?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I received a report from an agent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who said that a gigantic wolf would not hand you over until I came personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Holo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She left without saying a word after we brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the negotiations go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to obtain the rights that I expected Medio Trading would want most.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to collect 307,112 silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The king plans to reissue a severely depreciated version of the silver coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and we are to be paid with the cash value of 350,000 pieces at the time of delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hundred and fifty thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contract was to pay you five percent of our profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please confirm it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred and twenty silver coins. That is five percent of our profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It only amounted... to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Transportation costs for the coins\Nwe collected, taxes levied on those very coins,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the processing fee for the contract were all taken into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They imposed a rather excessive processing fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The King's advisors probably put him up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They had to give up those privileges, but they minimized their losses on the currency exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was beyond what we could foresee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to business, expect the unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Unexpected situations can work out happily as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Medio Trading was desperate for those special privileges.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were collecting silver coins that were guaranteed to depreciate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping them would be little different from holding a debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably wanted to turn any kind of profit at this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have to think twice about their offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One thousand for me, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it's a trifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Will silver coins be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd prefer payment in commodities, we can have that arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have pepper?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's light, compact, and as winter falls, its price will rise as meat becomes more popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. It just reminded me\Nof a particular play I recently read.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A religious play created by the Church to advocate restraint among traders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, the devil appeared in front of a wealthy merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bring forth the tastiest human around or I shall devour you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The merchant feared for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He offered a young maid and a fat serf, but the devil shook his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After searching across the town for a luscious human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he finally came across a boy who smelled of honey and milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the merchant offered the boy to the devil, the boy said,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"The tastiest human is right in front of you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What the devil saw was a man who ate spices daily,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and whose fattened soul was perfectly seasoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just imagining a fattened {*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}\Nbeing devoured by the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind having a body seasoned with spices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have many fruitful dealings in the future, {*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I must return to my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Lawrence{*Lawrence-san}, an invoice addressed to you has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall buying any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is the loading dock?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight ahead, make a right, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A robe, a silk sash, traveling shoes, a tortoiseshell comb,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and last but not least,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,tons of apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a total of a hundred and forty silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Holo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want you to come all the way to the northern woods just to collect on a debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll return home only after I've repaid you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Some spice and a wolf, huh?{now we truly are}{WOLF AND SPICE, HUH?}{This conveys what he actually means by this a little but is less of a title drop, but as far as I'm concerned that's two advantages}{A SPICY WOLF, HUH?}
